## Dependencies

CNVinject was developed and tested with:

- Python 3.12
- pysam 0.24.0
- samtools 1.19.2 using htslib 1.19
- bwa 0.7.17-r1188


Recommended installation steps (conda):

git clone <REPO_URL>
export PATH="<path/to>/cnvinject/bin:$PATH"  # add cnvinject/bin to path

cd path/to/CNVinject  # CNVinject top directory
conda env create -f environment.yml  # Create conda environment from provided yaml
conda activate cnvinject
cnvinject --help  #Ensure it is working

